# Guardian Skip

Guardian Skip is using the Drop AFK Method to Enter the boss arena and allow the player to skip the bossfight.

The skip is really precise and require frame perfect inputs.

\
The skip was found by San & splee5556 in Febuary 2026.

## **External Resources**

Demonstration [https://youtu.be/68AQBOO9mCw](https://youtu.be/68AQBOO9mCw) by San on YouTube
